<P>While I was regaling over my pigeon pye, &amp;c. a very decent elderly looking kind of man, a farmer, made his appearance, &s;eemingly communicative and intelligent, I a&s;ked him que&s;tions relative to the di&s;tance from Stamford, and what places were
